snippet.title: Blanc - Indie World Showcase 11.9.2022 - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Blanc is coming to Nintendo Switch on February 14, 2023. Pre-order today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/blanc-switch/

Blanc is an artistic cooperative adventure that follows the journey of a wolf cub and a fawn stranded in a vast, snowy wilderness. They must come together in an unlikely partnership to find their families.

#Blanc #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch
